Rashford, Herrera thrilled to beat Chelsea Posted , 2017-04-16 
Marcus Rashford and Ander Herrera were delighted after their goals helped Manchester United defeat Premier League leaders Chelsea at Old Trafford on Sunday, with the latter describing the team's display as 'almost perfect'.
